name: BUM CUM DOOR POSTERS
description:
With real new york city environments, each being unique in their own way giving you doors, roll down gates, billboards and more!

Each poster is laser printed on a super heavy matte white card stock in Ledger size (11x14) best for bleed control and mixed media usage.

name: BUM CUM VOLUME TWO - Chapter One
description:
In the second series of Bum Cum, I bring you more raw doors that've been crushed by artists you've come to see a lot of in the past year since the last zine.

Each zine is hand made measuring 4.25x5.5 printed on medium weight matte laser print paper tucked inside of a plastic sleeve.

Bum Cum Volume Two will be a three part series in itself that'll be released throughout 2014.

UPDATE!

Each zine comes with one of many bum cum posters email bumcumnyc@gmail.com if you'd like a specific one.

name: BUM CUM VOLUME ONE
description:
Bheir and Bum Cum teamed up to create a 48 paged zine based on graffiti doors using full black and white photographs that've been taken over the past year in both the lower east side of manhattan and brooklyn.


This zine comes with two stickers from one of the following artists. Jec FAA, Wack FAA, Decoy FAA, Dick Mama, and Kosby ATM
